snippet.textDisplay:
Goosebumps, SubhanAllah, Brilliant.  
- Atif, Rohail, Coke Studio Pakistan team you guys did just to Khan Shahab.  
- And that addition of Darood at the end was out of the world experience - "Jahan pay Allah ka zikr aata hai, Uske Mehboob ﷺ ka bhi zikr aata hai."
- Atif almost pulled this Hamd as an unplugged version, thanks to Atif's voice and Rohail's planning. I cried remembering Khan  Shahab. Thank you so much, guys. 
- Rohail Hyatt, I thank Allah you came back. I hope you know how much we have missed you. 

Thank you, we are expecting so much from the season. In sha Allah Rohail will release great and greater numbers in this tenure.
